creator: Magic Life PL
descriptionHtml:
Magic Shield is a brand protection and anti-counterfeiting solution incorporated by MagicLife using bank-graded unique QR code technology. Users can scan the product QR code through this application to quickly verify the authenticity. The app ensures that users use official authentic products to obtain a safe and secure consumer experience . How to use?
1) Download this app
2) Register for a user account
3) Activate the scan function of the app
4) Scan the QR code on the product security label
5) Follow the instructions stated in the app
6) If the product is real, you will receive the scanned message as congratulation for successful authentication. If the product is suspicious, you will receive a warning message.
